      <div>
        <h1 class="text">Resistance</h1>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">We are an identity that cannot be summed up.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">We drink from the roots of a leafy ceiba,<br>that defends, like a mother bear,<br>her people, and resists<br>the malice of the greedy,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">who shamelessly want to seize<br>this land, which only has many mountains,<br>a nature without end, surrounded by a dolphin<br>who always dances, watching over us.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">We Cubans resist, we joke about everything—<br>even our nightmares that keep us from sleeping.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">We make a song out of it and dance,<br>shaking off our sorrows,<br>the poverty in our homes.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">We still have our laughter,<br>our mischief stands out.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Our Lady of Charity watches over us,<br>and to her we pray so that things go well,</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">maybe for a trip,<br>or a project, or for the healing<br>of our brother—<br>to be able to offer a hand to a stranger,<br>to drink the nectar of sugarcane,<br>to live our lives without malice—</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">because evil returns,<br>so say the orishas who live among us.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Our religion is a stew,<br>where diverse wisdoms mix.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">Ortiz would say we are a melting pot,<br>where experiences merge through<br>beliefs in our freedom.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">We are peace and truth,<br>there, where they seek us without regret or surprise—</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="text">to embrace the one who cries on my shoulder,<br>to care for our traditions, which are passions<br>that help us survive.</p>
      </div>

